Install:
	make install


Hey, come on... it's a small perl script. Simply copy it to a warm and
comfortable place like /usr/local/bin and be shure to give it executable
rights.

Prerequisitories:
  - Perl (tested with Perl 5.8.3 but should work with every version)
  - Net::NNTP module (avaliable at http://www.cpan.org)

